---
import StarlightPage from '@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro';
---

<StarlightPage frontmatter={{ title: 'Idep Documentation', template: 'splash' }}>

<style is:global>
  /* Hide the auto-rendered page title that appears before hero-wrap */
  h1:not(.hero-title) {
    display: none !important;
  }

  .hero-wrap {
    padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sl-color-hairline);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sl-color-accent) 10%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--sl-color-accent) 30%, transparent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-variation-settings: 'WONK' 1, 'opsz' 144;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-title .accent {
    color: var(--sl-color-accent);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--sl-color-accent);
    color: #0F0D0B;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-hairline);
  }

  /* Cards */
  .cards-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 3.5rem auto 0;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--sl-color-bg-nav);
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-hairline);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--sl-color-accent); }

  .card-icon {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }

  .card-desc {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Version strip */
  .version-strip {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem 0;
  }
  .version-strip a {
    color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>

<div class="hero-wrap">
  <span class="hero-eyebrow">v0.0.2 · Pre-alpha · Apache 2.0</span>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    The IDE that<br/>
    thinks <span class="accent">with</span> you
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-sub">
    Rust-native, local-first, any AI backend.<br/>
    Your codebase never leaves your machine.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="/getting-started/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started →</a>
    <a href="/configuration/" class="btn btn-secondary">Configuration</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/idep-editor/idep" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub ↗</a>
  </div>
</div>

<section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 4rem auto 0; padding: 0 2rem;">
  <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Overview</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--sl-color-gray-2); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    Idep is a Rust-native AI-powered IDE with local-first architecture. Connect any AI backend — Ollama for local inference, Anthropic for Claude, HuggingFace, or OpenAI-compatible endpoints. Your codebase never leaves your machine. v0.0.2 ships with end-to-end completions and chat streaming.
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">What's New in v0.0.2</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div style="padding: 1rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--sl-color-accent); background: var(--sl-color-bg-nav); border-radius: 6px;">
      <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1rem;">Completions</h3>
      <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--sl-color-gray-2); font-size: 0.95rem;">CompletionEngine wired to llm-ls LSP bridge. Configurable debounce (default 300ms), stop-sequence handling, FIM token validation for DeepSeek, StarCoder, CodeLlama.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding: 1rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--sl-color-accent); background: var(--sl-color-bg-nav); border-radius: 6px;">
      <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1rem;">Chat</h3>
      <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--sl-color-gray-2); font-size: 0.95rem;">Streaming token callback on send(). Debounce wired through to chat context for responsive interactions.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="padding: 1rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--sl-color-accent); background: var(--sl-color-bg-nav); border-radius: 6px;">
      <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1rem;">Core APIs</h3>
      <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--sl-color-gray-2); font-size: 0.95rem;">Buffer API (insert, delete, lines, to_string), cursor tracking, Workspace::open_file/save_file, file watcher with auto-reindex.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Quick Start</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--sl-color-gray-2); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Clone, build, configure your backend, and run your first completion in minutes.</p>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <a href="/getting-started/" class="card" style="padding: 1.25rem; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;">
      <div style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--sl-color-accent); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">→</div>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);">Getting Started</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);">Prerequisites, build, config setup</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/configuration/" class="card" style="padding: 1.25rem; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;">
      <div style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--sl-color-accent); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">⚙</div>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);">Configuration</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);">Config reference and backends</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/architecture/" class="card" style="padding: 1.25rem; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;">
      <div style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--sl-color-accent); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">◇</div>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--sl-color-gray-1);">Architecture</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);">Crate map and design</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<p class="version-strip">
  Current release: <a href="https://github.com/idep-editor/idep/releases/tag/v0.0.2">v0.0.2</a>
  · <a href="https://github.com/idep-editor/idep/blob/main/TODO.md">Roadmap</a>
  · <a href="https://idep.dev">idep.dev ↗</a>
</p>

</StarlightPage>
